ientation.html\">TDDUI ServiceRequest DemandeOrientation</a></p></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"RelatedPerson1-13\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>RelatedPerson</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Ressource FHIR coeur</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/relatedperson.html\">RelatedPerson</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profils supportés</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-related-person-contact.html\">TDDUI RelatedPerson Contact</a></p></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Observation1-14\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Observation</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Ressource FHIR coeur</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/observation.html\">Observation</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profils supportés</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-observation-cause-mortalite.html\">TDDUI Observation Cause Mortalite</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-observation-periode-scolaire.html\">TDDUI Observation Periode Scolaire</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-observation-mobilite-usager.html\">TDDUI Observation Mobilite Usager</a><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-observation-repas.html\">TDDUI Observation Repas</a></p></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Schedule1-15\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Schedule</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Ressource FHIR coeur</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/schedule.html\">Schedule</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profils supportés</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-schedule.html\">TDDUI Schedule</a></p></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Slot1-16\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Slot</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Ressource FHIR coeur</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/slot.html\">Slot</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profils supportés</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-slot-presence-absence.html\">TDDUI Slot Presence Absence</a></p></div></div><p/></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Basic1-17\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Conformité de la ressource : unspecified </span>Basic</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Ressource FHIR coeur</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/basic.html\">Basic</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Politique de référence</span><br/></div><div class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"lead\">Résumé des interactions</span><br/><ul><li>Supporte <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Profils supportés</span><p><a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-basic-decision.html\">TDDUI Basic Decision</a></p></div></div><p/></div></div></div></div><div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: CapabilityStatement TDDUIConsommateur</b></p><a name=\"en-TDDUIConsommateur\"> </a><a name=\"en-hcTDDUIConsommateur\"> </a><h2 id=\"en-title\">TDDUI-Consommateur</h2><ul><li>Implementation Guide Version: 2.4.0 </li><li>FHIR Version: 4.0.1 </li><li>Supported Formats: <code>application/fhir+xml</code>, <code>application/fhir+json</code></li><li>Published on: 2024-06-20 09:51:35+0200 </li><li>Published by: ANS </li></ul><blockquote class=\"impl-note\"><p><strong>Note to Implementers: FHIR Capabilities</strong></p><p>Any FHIR capability may be 'allowed' by the system unless explicitly marked as 'SHALL NOT'. A few items are marked as MAY in the Implementation Guide to highlight their potential relevance to the use case.</p></blockquote><h3 id=\"en-shallIGs\">SHALL Support the Following Implementation Guides</h3><ul><li>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/tddui</li></ul><h2 id=\"en-rest\">FHIR RESTful Capabilities</h2><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h3 id=\"en-mode1\" class=\"panel-title\">Mode: <code>client</code></h3></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div><p>Réception de données transmises depuis un logiciel DUI (flux 1).</p>\n</div><div class=\"lead\"><em>Security</em></div><blockquote><div><p>L’ANS propose des référentiels dédiés à la politique de sécurité (la PGSSI-S) et des mécanismes de sécurisation sont définis dans les volets de la couche Transport du Cadre d’Interopérabilité des systèmes d’information de santé (CI-SIS)</p>\n</div></blockquote><div class=\"lead\"><em>Summary of System-wide Interactions</em></div><ul><li>Supports the <code>transaction</code>interaction described as follows:<div><p>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/tddui/StructureDefinition/tddui-bundle</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div><h3 id=\"en-resourcesCap1\">Capabilities by Resource/Profile</h3><h4 id=\"en-resourcesSummary1\">Summary</h4><p>The summary table lists the resources that are part of this configuration, and for each resource it lists:</p><ul><li>The relevant profiles (if any)</li><li>The interactions supported by each resource (<b><span class=\"bg-info\">R</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">S</span></b>earch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">U</span></b>pdate, and <b><span class=\"bg-info\">C</span></b>reate, are always shown, while <b><span class=\"bg-info\">VR</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">P</span></b>atch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">D</span></b>elete, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">I</span></b>nstance, or <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">T</span></b>ype are only present if at least one of the resources has support for them.</li><li><span>The required, recommended, and some optional search parameters (if any). </span></li><li>The linked resources enabled for <code>_include</code></li><li>The other resources enabled for <code>_revinclude</code></li><li>The operations on the resource (if any)</li></ul><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th><b>Resource Type</b></th><th><b>Profile</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET a resource (read interaction)\">R</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET all set of resources of the type (search interaction)\">S</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"PUT a new resource version (update interaction)\">U</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"POST a new resource (create interaction)\">C</b></th><th><b title=\"Required and recommended search parameters\">Searches</b></th><th><code><b>_include</b></code></th><th><code><b>_revinclude</b></code></th><th><b>Operations</b></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Patient1-1\">Patient</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-patient.html\">TDDUI Patient</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-patient-ins.html\">TDDUI Patient INS</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Organization1-2\">Organization</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-organization.html\">TDDUI Organization</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Encounter1-3\">Encounter</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-encounter-sejour.html\">TDDUI Encounter Sejour</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-encounter-evenement.html\">TDDUI Encounter Evenement</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Practitioner1-4\">Practitioner</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-practitioner.html\">TDDUI Practitioner</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-PractitionerRole1-5\">PractitionerRole</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-practitioner-role.html\">TDDUI Practitioner Role</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Task1-6\">Task</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-transport-professionnel.html\">TDDUI Task Transport Professionnel</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-transport-usager.html\">TDDUI Task Transport Usager</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-action.html\">TDDUI Task Action</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-bilan.html\">TDDUI Task Bilan</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-moyen-ressource.html\">TDDUI Task MoyenRessource</a><br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-task-prestation.html\">TDDUI Task Prestation</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-QuestionnaireResponse1-7\">QuestionnaireResponse</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-questionnaire-response.html\">TDDUI QuestionnaireResponse</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-DocumentReference1-8\">DocumentReference</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-document-reference.html\">TDDUI DocumentReference</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-CarePlan1-9\">CarePlan</a></td><td>Supported Profiles<br/>  <a href=\"StructureDefinition-tddui-careplan-projet-personnalise.html\">TDDUI CarePlan Projet Personalise</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class